<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spanish_Inquisition&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Henry_Charles_Lea" title="Henry Charles Lea">Henry Charles Lea</a>, <i>A History of the Inquisition of Spain</i> (4 volumes), (New York and London, 1906–1907).</li>
