<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=R._Sabbatini&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="R. Sabbatini (page does not exist)">R. Sabbatini</a>, “Torquemada and the Spanish Inquisition,” (1913).</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=C._Roth&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="C. Roth (page does not exist)">C. Roth</a>, “The Spanish Inquisition,” (1937).</li>
